English(en): Tiger: Think about it as a bribe.
Me: I’ll give you some rice cake!
Me: I’ll give you another one!

Korean(ko): 호랑이: 난 당장 배가 고프단 말이다!

English(en): Me: I’ll give you a rice cake, so please look at it!

Korean(ko): 나: 난 이렇게 죽는구나! 세상아 안녕!
English(en): Me: This is how I die! Bye world!

Korean(ko): 호랑이: 몇 개나 줄 수 있는데?
English(en): Tiger: How many can you give me?

Korean(ko): 나: 집에 많아요! 집에만 다녀오게 해주세요!
English(en): Me: I have a lot at home! Please just let me go home!
